recibe en Main

local hParameters := build_gets( AP_ARGS() )
local cUrl

function build_gets( cValues )
   local hValues := { => }
   local aParts := hb_ATokens( cValues, GETVARS_SEPARATOR )
   local aPart, cPart
   local cKey, cValue

   for each cPart in aParts
      aPart = hb_ATokens( cPart, GETVARS_ASSIGN )
      if Len( aPart ) > GETVARS_KEY
         cKey = aPart[ GETVARS_KEY ]
         cValue = aPart[ GETVARS_VALUE ]
         hValues[ cKey ] = cValue
         ? cValue, cKey
      end
   next

return hValues

#define GETVARS_SEPARATOR "&"
#define GETVARS_ASSIGN "="
#define GETVARS_KEY 1
#define GETVARS_VALUE 2
